Open Source

  • Currency Converter

    Calculates money quick and easy way to see live foreign exchange rates.

    Based on swift 3.0, VIPER and special thanks to hakanensari for conversion API

  • Loan EMI Calculator

    Calculate your Equated Monthly instalment (EMI) for Home loan, Housing loan, Car loan & Personal loan.

    Based on Uncle Bob’s clean architecture approach and special thanks to clean-swift

  • TIP Calculator

    Calculate your tip and split the bill between any number of people.

    Based on viper architecture of objective-c VIPER and apple auto layout

  • Sip Calculator

    SIP calculator calculates the future value of SIP (Systematic Investment Plan) payments.

    Based on simple apple swift language
